---
title: Teriyaki Beef Meatballs on Garlic Rice with Japanese Slaw
description: This dish is super simple and packed with delectable flavours. The colourful slaw will surprise you with its Japanese vibes and sweet crunchy veggies!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/teriyaki-beef-meatballs-01ce6684.jpg
